 Sorbitol MacConkey w Cefixime Tellurite (CT-SMAC) 
 
 For selective and differential isolation of enterohemorrhagic Escherichia coli O157.
 
 For SMAC - 
 Dissolve 25.75g SMAC (oxoid - CM0813) in 500 ml dH2O
 Autoclave
 
 Once cooled so not painful to touch, add cefixime tellurite (Oxoid - SR0172) next to the flame (2 ml to 500 ml SMAC)
 
 Pour plates next to flame and allow to cool before storing (upside down).
 Will keep in fridge for ~ 2 weeks. 
 
